Add fade transitions for scene/state switches

A black curtain in the HUD fades in on every scene load and is faded out
before switching, so the one real hitch (the scene rebuild when returning to
the menu) happens behind black instead of on screen. PLAY, Stack Again, and
Main Menu all fade through it now. The wrappers are async; _start_game and
_on_restart stay synchronous so the test tools are unaffected.

